    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely, keeping the <strong>whites</strong> and <strong>greens</strong> separate</p><p>Grate your <strong>apple[s]</strong> (skin on) into a bowl</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1621863966972-x200.jpg",
