        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> meat-free mince </strong>(remove the paper if required!),<strong> chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>sliced spring onion whites</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong> and 2 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span> <strong>brown</strong> <strong>sugar</strong> to the grated apple and mix thoroughly with clean hands – this is your <strong>Korean-style meat-free mince</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
