        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> Korean-style meat-free mince</strong> and the <strong>halved green beans</strong></p><p>Spread the mixture out and cook for 4 min, without stirring</p>",
