    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Flip the mince, and cook for a further 4 min on the other side</p><p>Once cooked, break up the <strong>mince</strong> into rough bite-sized pieces with a wooden spoon – this is your <strong>Korean-style meat-free</strong> <strong>mince</strong> <strong>bulgogi with green beans</strong></p>",
