      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Korean-style meat-free</strong> <strong>mince</strong> <strong>bulgogi with green beans </strong>with the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
